snippet.title: The Media SIDED With Amber Heard? Bias Against Johnny Depp!
snippet.description:
The Amber Heard supporters are here for some reason 😂

The clear as day media bias has got to stop and the only way we can make that stop is to voice our opinions in practical ways. No spam, no threats. 2021 shall be Johnny  Depps year and not Ambers!

My Amber Heard Saga playlist! https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLWh7zSa4b9BE8PDsYJ_EZozyaIF3DXNfl

Join the notification club on Discord for more reliable notifications and updates for when I upload! https://discord.gg/yRFkxRpzYt

Instagram Link : https://www.instagram.com/mister_mcfab/

Outro Song Credits Adam Joseph : https://youtu.be/4Tyval51ML4

#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
